prove T is monotonic （你可以寫條式出黎d左佢睇下咩樣，我懶得計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果唔係monotonic，T(L)同T(0)邊個大d都係同上面一樣depends on M/m，但可能佢行第一步(i.e. for small x)個陣係一定increase或者一定decrease，不過都係唔知點prove"},{"pid":"22254d3bc4d0d66d73d95e3f23889252627f3215","tid":2425768,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a7e4b09f7b597ae3ff3b415d25c06f626bd347","tid":2425768,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff450cdc2fbf9eb93ea8f5f8039ae2785ca98182","tid":2425768,"uid":108770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db23f5def9edf4665a45d93188e6bac0a386bf93","tid":2425768,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T20:33:50.000Z","msg":"佢企P個陣你可以當有兩條繩拉住，所以左邊應該係2T"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"咁點解（ii)會岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該要睇M/m幾大<br />\ndefine x = 由pivot計起行左幾多，T(x)係個人係x個陣既tension，L係塊板長度<br />\n直覺覺得T(x)係monotonic, 而<br />\nT(0) = Mg/2<br />\n2T(L) = Mg/2 + mg<br />\n即係T(L) = Mg/4 + mg/2 <br />\nT(L)-T(0) = mg/2 - Mg/4 = (2mg-Mg)/4<br />\nif M/m &lt; 2 then T(L) &gt; T(0)<br />\nif M/m &gt; 2 then T(L) &lt; T(0)<br />\n所以如果T係monotonic咁T係可以increase可以decrease<br />\n但我唔知點prove T is monotonic （你可以寫條式出黎d左佢睇下咩樣，我懶得計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果唔係monotonic，T(L)同T(0)邊個大d都係同上面一樣depends on M/m，但可能佢行第一步(i.e. for small x)個陣係一定increase或者一定decrease，不過都係唔知點prove"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"同埋佢有樣野無講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢向左行個陣keep唔keep the plank horizontal"},{"pid":"03e938962a259c3a3c3215e7c8befb1e3895a970","tid":2425768,"uid":108770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a7e4b09f7b597ae3ff3b415d25c06f626bd347","tid":2425768,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike"